lead_paragraph: Midfielder Jack Wilshere will be offered a new Arsenal contract despite being sent to Bournemouth on loan this season, the London club's manager Arsene Wenger said on Friday.

headline.print_headline: Wilshere Will Be Offered New Arsenal Deal, Says Wenger
headline.main: Wilshere Will Be Offered New Arsenal Deal, Says Wenger
